reviews.comments:
Angela was a great host. Quick to respond to messages and very knowledgeable about area. Lovely welcome pack and provision of bathroom/laundry/kitchen supplies were great and very much appreciated.
Condo PROS - 
- great location, close enough to Waikiki and other central attractions, but far enough away that you’re not affected by the ‘action’;
- kitchen is well equipped for a couple or small family;
- bathroom functions well, but dated;
- access to washer/dryer.
CONS
- showerhead need attention;
- linen supply not enough for family;
- no beach supplies;
- washer/dryer are super noisey;
- tv issues - no movies as advertised, small number of available channels;
- building security super unhelpful - not there for ABNB residents.
